snippet.textDisplay: It started with Tu Jhoom. Came full circle with Mehmaan. The fundamental job of any CEO is to take the brand that’s in their charge to a better place than where they found it. Thank you Xulfi for growing the Coke Studio brand so much during the last two seasons. Not just incrementally, but through a fundamental rethink of CS as an all original audio visual experience.
